Security: Public / Private RSA
    Each user shares public keys with contact
    Public keys stored in one file
    
Taking an image
    Open image window
    On capture
        Get approval
            Accepted
                Choose n contacts
                    Encrypt n images using n public keys
                    Ship files to recipients
            Reject
                Return to capture
Viewing file
    on mouse down
        decrypt file to memory
        display using opencv
        start timer
    on mouse release
        delete image from screen
        delete the memory contents
    on timer finish
        delete image from screen
        delete the memory contents
        delete encrypted content
        
    on screen capture key input
        delete image from screen
        delete the memory contents
        delete encrypted content
        end timer
        scold user